extends layout

block head
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="/about.css")

block content
  h2 #{title} 
  p This page is here to give you a short run down of what is happening in this project. Our goal is to create a very simple solution to many people's problems. We want a place where you can get information easily and reliably.

  h3 Meet the Team

  .about
    .profile
      img(src="https://via.placeholder.com/150", alt="Person 1")
      h3 Editor 1
      p Editor 1 is a dedicated content creator and editor who works tirelessly to ensure the website provides accurate and reliable information to users.

    .profile
      img(src="https://via.placeholder.com/150", alt="Person 2")
      h3 Editor 2
      p Editor 2 is a skilled writer and editor who brings their expertise to create engaging content that keeps users coming back for more.

    .profile
      img(src="https://via.placeholder.com/150", alt="Person 3")
      h3 Creator 1
      p Creator 1 is a talented web developer who designed and built the website, ensuring it is user-friendly and easy to navigate.

    .profile
      img(src="https://via.placeholder.com/150", alt="Person 4")
      h3 Creator 2
      p Creator 2 is a creative visionary who came up with the concept for the website and guided its development, ensuring it meets users' needs.

  p Our team is dedicated to providing an exceptional user experience and making sure that the content on the website is up-to-date, relevant, and engaging. We are constantly working to improve the site and expand its offerings, so be sure to check back often for new updates and features.
